metadata.description:
In the centre of the painting is Pepe and Stan Lee, who is conducting Pepe's coronation ceremony. The coronation is blessed by Boba Fett, who is also present in the painting.

The painting depicts the whole ceremony in its entirety. All of Pepe's best friends who came to the party are present in the painting.
